cdbDeleteDoc            package:R4CouchDB            R Documentation

_D_e_l_e_t_e_s _a _d_o_c_u_m_e_n_t _f_r_o_m _a _d_a_t_a_b_a_s_e

_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     With a given 'cdb$id' this function sends a http '"DELETE"'
     request to the url '.../cdb$id?rev=cdb$rev'.

_U_s_a_g_e:

     cdbDeleteDoc(cdb)

_A_r_g_u_m_e_n_t_s:

     cdb: Beside 'cdb$serverName', 'cdb$port' and 'cdb$DBName' the
          'cdb$id' must be given. R errors are reported    in
          'cdb$errors' 

_V_a_l_u_e:

    cdb : The result of the delete request is stored in
          'cdb$res'(whatever this means). 

